{"tid":765861,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個爛到爆既gag","createTime":"2018-08-03T06:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T11:02:00.000Z","uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"05d9548d3fb8e90a4d3899777c6bd77d7a322d24","tid":765861,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"古代時<br />\n宮廷上有位老臣子大叫：「皇上息怒！ 皇上息怒！」<br />\n皇上：「朕冇事！哈哈哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n點知，成個皇宮d 人都燒死晒<br />\n因為冇熄爐，燒撚死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n韜韜突然走出黎大叫：<br />\n「喺個爐要安全呀！」<br />\n\t<br />\n「嗱，如果用卡式石油氣爐一定要有GU標誌，入氣嗰陣，個凹位要向上， <br />\n兩個爐千祈唔好平排放，唔好亂用配件， 個煲咪大過個爐面呀。 <br />\n個爐安全咯，食乜都好味啲啦！ 」<br />\n<br />\n突然！<br />\n果然翁亂入：<br />\n「你又話啲料最緊要既。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韜韜：「打邊爐就唔同，冇個爐，點打呀！」"},{"pid":"c8f022bcc4d71604cc9f1c82c1a2deab9cf9e595","tid":765861,"uid":32694,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"有聲⋯⋯<br />\n係咪得我一個覺得好好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177a664d0291d6f9e6fd2e61c8785189dfac2fac","tid":765861,"uid":154218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"5dc791f73abb9eea5673ad8677092088b367008b","tid":765861,"uid":164682,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"d390b6e3d5d15e659e9715b26cb4290daaab9587","tid":765861,"uid":8677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61cc80d50f804eafea69d408af6496415952268","tid":765861,"uid":12458,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"諗起鄭則士大嗌 「微臣董昭先行告退！！！」"},{"pid":"b4f4c6feae480ca80386c57fb630b54bc8248b88","tid":765861,"uid":123335,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c